title: JAM Replay Wireless Speaker
description: Prepare to be amazed the first time you press play — with JAM Replay, you get booming sound from a speaker the size of a baseball. (Seriously, the bass is nuts!) With its compact size and rubberized exterior, it’s perfect to toss in your bag and take along for the ride.
